race.description: Slattery / Nutrien Harcourt Qtis Maiden Plate
race.comment: PERFECT WORK (4) returns after 12 weeks in the paddock. Closed the last campaign with a fourth over 1100m at Charleville. Looks the one to beat. MADAM MAGPIE (9) finished sixth at her last appearance over 1050m at Rockhampton on November 3. Finds a suitable assignment this time and is a great chance to break through. KABUKICHO (6) has put together back-to-back placings, the latest when 0.8 lengths away in third over 1000m at Mitchell. Likely improver with strong prospects. REPLICA (10) finished 9 lengths away in 12th at her last appearance over 1400m at Eagle Farm on September 24. Expected to feature in the finish this time.
